nformed, and data-driven, so firm leaders can spend their time doing what they love. Learn more at <a class=\"ProsemirrorEditor-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.bqe.com\/who-we-serve\/engineering?utm_source=emi&amp;utm_medium=webinar&amp;utm_campaign=emiartoffeesweb-enghome-2025610\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">www.bqe.com<\/a>.<\/p>","align":"center","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"},{"id":"466d622","settings":{"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","pa_condition_repeater":[]},"elements":[{"id":"40e9206e","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null,"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[{"id":"56a5c4ba","settings":{"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","pa_condition_repeater":[]},"elements":[{"id":"6e9712b1","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null,"space_between_widgets":0,"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[{"id":"763cfe95","settings":{"editor":"<p class=\"fl-heading\"><span class=\"fl-heading-text\">Summary<\/span><\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"a1fdb57","settings":{"editor":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.bqe.com\/who-we-serve\/engineering?utm_source=emi&amp;utm_medium=webinar&amp;utm_campaign=emiartoffeesweb-enghome-2025610\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-74123\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/art-of-estimating-fees-webinar--300x200.jpg\" alt=\"The Art of Estimating Fees\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" \/><\/a>Ready to master the art of estimating fees and gain profound insights into their impact on your bottom line? Join Douglas Teiger, FAIA, on a journey that begins at the very inception of a project\u2014when that initial request for a proposal lands on your desk or in your inbox. In this comprehensive session, you will not only learn to define project scope, but also develop a Rough Order of Magnitude (ROM) for construction costs and estimate project hours. We'll culminate by dissecting how fees are structured and introduce a simplified system to enhance your overall project profitability.<\/p><p>Join Douglas for this illuminating session that will empower you to unlock profitable projects and gain mastery in fee estimation. By the end of this session, you'll possess the knowledge and tools to make informed financial decisions, ensuring the prosperity of your AE firm.<\/p><p><strong>By the end of this session, you will learn how to:<\/strong><\/p><ol><li>Identify the correlation between project scope, estimated project cost, and fee<\/li><li>Develop a Rough Order of Magnitude (ROM) for construction costs in a simple way<\/li><li>Create a top-down approach to fee estimation based on percentage of costs as a guideline<\/li><li>Estimate fees, whether they are for hourly or fixed-fee projects<\/li><li>Define the allocation of hours for each project phase and develop strategies to effectively manage them<\/li><\/ol><p><!-- \/wp:fl-builder\/layout --><\/p>","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"9a27c73","settings":{"editor":"<p class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Your Speaker<\/b><\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"30","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"2782f184","settings":{"editor":"<h2 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Douglas Teiger, FAIA | Founder, Teiger Consulting<\/h2>","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"46b52df6","settings":{"editor":"<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.bqe.com\/who-we-serve\/engineering?utm_source=emi&amp;utm_medium=webinar&amp;utm_campaign=emiartoffeesweb-enghome-2025610\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-74122\" title=\"Douglas Teiger, FAIA \" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Douglas-Teiger-Headshot.jpg\" alt=\"bqe\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" \/><\/a><\/p><p>Douglas graduated from Cornell University, in 1982 with a BARCH.\u00a0 He opened his own firm in 1989 and grew from a solo practitioner to become managing partner of his 32-person firm.\u00a0\u00a0<\/p><p>In 2009, Douglas received a Master\u2019s in Spiritual Psychology from USM, where he learned tools and skills he is sharing with his staff and clients. His ability to effectively streamline the operations allowed for more time to be spent on design and project research while creating a culture that fosters a holistic approach to a work life balance.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/p><p>In 2017, he served as President of the AIA Los Angeles Chapter and previously served on the AIA National Strategic Council. In 2019 Douglas transitioned out of his firm elevating three associates to partners, sold his shares and started his next venture, Teiger Consulting.\u00a0\u00a0<\/p><p>Douglas\u2019s mission is to \u201clive an inspiring balanced life\u201d whether it involves family, coaching, consulting, painting, or sports.\u00a0\u00a0<\/p>","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"63b03d8","settings":{"editor":"<p class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Your Host<\/b><\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"30","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"57a29b23","settings":{"editor":"<h2 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Fiona Johann, PMP, AEC PM | Engineering Management Institute<\/h2>","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"69973187","settings":{"editor":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Fiona-Johann.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-73855 alignright\" title=\"Fiona Johann, PMP, AEC PM\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Fiona-Johann.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" \/><\/a><\/p><p>With years of experience in higher education honing leadership skills among faculty, Fiona Johann now partners with AEC engineers to help them become outstanding project managers and leaders. Drawing on her PMP certification and extensive background in leadership development, she equips professionals with the tools and strategies needed to excel in project delivery and team management.<\/p>","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"100","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"section"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"}],"settings":{"template":"elementor_canvas"},"metadata":{"_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes":"4","_yoast_wpseo_content_score":"30","be_title_toggle_hide":"1","disable_sitewide_popup":"a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"true\";}","_yoast_wpseo_wordproof_timestamp":"","_yoast_wpseo_meta-robots-noindex":"1","_yoast_wpseo_meta-robots-nofollow":"1"}}